name: ChlamydiaTrachomatisInfectionTestsForChlamydiaTrachomatisNucleicAcid
title: Chlamydia trachomatis Infection (Tests for Chlamydia trachomatis Nucleic Acid)
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test names associated with detecting the presence of Chlamydia trachomatis nucleic acid),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: component: Chlamydia trachomatis nucleic acid;  

LOINC search:  'Chlamydia trachomatis nucleic acid -panel -donor'),(Exclusion Criteria: LOINC SYSTEM = Donor and panel tests)
